quran[78]{c,v,t}:
  22,1,"Eey monyo yim…ďe, kulee Joomi mo'on, pellet, dillannde Darnga ngo ko hu'unde mawnde."
  22,2,"√Ďande nji'oton ngal, njejjitoyay kala muyninoowo ko o muyninaynoo ko, fukka kala cowii…óo ko o sowiinoo kon, a yi'at yim…ďe …ďen no manndili, hara kam…ďe …ďe manndiaa, kono Lepte Alla …óen ko sa…ótu…óe."
  22,3,"No e yim…ďe …ďe on mo no wennja e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal, o jokka kala Seytaane canndallo."
  22,4,"Winndaama e hoore-makko won'de pellet, kala beldu…óo e makko pellet, o majjinat mo, o …óowa mo haa ka Lepte Sa'iiri."
  22,5,"Ey mon yim…ďe, si tawii on e cikkatiima immorde e immital ngal, pellet, Minen Min Tagii on immorde e mbullaari refti e to…ď…ďere maniiyu, refti e he…ó…óere refti e husre timmunde tagoore e nde wonaa timmunde tagoore fii yo Min …ďannginan on, Mi…óen √Ďii…ďina ka renngaaji ko Min Muuyi kon haa e happu innaa…óo, refti Min njaltini on ko on booboo…ďe, refti fii yo on njotto sagatalaaku mo'on no e mo'on …ďen …ďe no maaya no e mo'on kadi …ďen …ďe no nduttee fa'ade ka …ďuri ja'asde e nguurndam …óam fii wota …ďe nganndu …ďaawo ganndal hay e hu'unde. A yi'at leydi ndin ko yo'orundi si Min njippinii e dow mayri ndiyam …óan ndi dilla ndi ∆īura ndi fu…óina immorde e kala noone woo…óu…óo."
  22,6,"∆äum, ko tawde pellet, Alla ko KaŇčko woni Goonga kan, pellet, O wurtinat maay…ďe …ďen, tawde pellet, ko O kattan…óo e dow kala hu'unde."
  22,7,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aray ngal sikke alaa e maggal, won'de pellet, Alla immintinay …ďen won'…ďe ka genaale."
  22,8,"No e yim…ďe …ďen on mo no wee√Īdaa e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal wonaa peewal wonaa deftere nur…óunde(jalbunde)."
  22,9,"Hkf…óo balaaji mu'un [mawnintinii…óo] fii yo o majjin gah Laawol Alla ngol, no woodani mo ka aduna koyeere Min mee…óinoyay mo kadi √Ďande Darngal Lepte cumoowe ngen."
  22,10,"∆äum ko sabu ko juu…óe maa…óa …óen ngardini kon. E won'de pellet, Alla wonaani Too√Īoowo jeyaa…ďe …ďen."
  22,11,"No e yim…ďe …ďen on mo no rewa Alla e dow selindaare; si mo∆ī∆īere he…ďii mo o tabitira sabu …óuum si jarrabuyee kadi he…ďii mo o waylitoo e ye'eso makko, o hayrii aduna on e La'akara on ko …óum tigi woni hayrere …ďanngunde nden."
  22,12,"Homo rewa gah Alla ko lorrataa mo e ko nafataa mo kadi. ∆äuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo], ko …óum woni majjere wo…ó…óunde nden."
  22,13,"Homo rewa on mo lorra mum no …ďuri …ďadaade diini nafa mum kan, bonii welddi…óo bonii kadi wuuridaa…óo."
  22,14,"Pellet, Alla homoo naatna …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īi …óin Aljannaaji no ila sengo ley majji caatlii …ói, pellet, Alla homo wa…óa ko o faandii ko."
  22,15,"On gon…óo no sikka won'de Alla wallataa mo ka aduna e ka La'akara; yo o fortu …ďoggol fa'ade ka kammu refti o ta∆īa ngol yo o ndaaru taw si pewje makko …óen ittay ko tikkani ko."
  22,16,"Ko wano nii Min nJippiniri …óe Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe. Pellet, Alla homo Feewna on Mo o muuyii."
  22,17,"Pellet, …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe e …ďen Yahuudinkoo…ďe e Saabi'iyaŇčkoo…ďe e AnnasaaraŇčkoo…ďe e MajuusiŇčkoo…ďe e …ďen sirkoo…ďe, pellet, Alla O ceerndoowo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Ďande Darngal. Pellet, Alla e dow kala hu'unde ko O Seedii…óo."
  22,18,"Enee a yi'aali, won'dema Alla no sujjan'de Mo …ďe won'…ďe ka kammuuji e …ďe won'…ďe ka leydi, na'ange nge kadi e lewru ndun e koode …óen e pelle …óen e le…ó…óe …óen e daabeeji …óin e ko …óuu…ói immorde e yim…ďe …ďen, ko …óuu…ói kadi wajibike e mu'un Lepte …óen. Kala mo Alla hoyni alanaa mo teddinoowo, pellet Alla homo golla ko o muuyi kon."
  22,19,"∆Āee …óoo …ói…óo ko wee√Īdondir…ďe, …ďe mbe√Īdondirii fii Joomi ma…ď…ďe …ďen yeddu…ďe non, ta∆īanoyte …ďe comci immorde e Yiite fatu…óam yuppee ka dow ko'e ma…ď…ďe."
  22,20,"Ha…óam honciniree(tayniree) ko woni kon ka deedi ma…ď…ďe e guri …óin kadi."
  22,21,"No woodani …ďoon…óe e jam…óe."
  22,22,"Tuma kala …ďe cokli jaltugol ndeer ton immorde e suno, …ďe nduttee e ndeer magge, […ďe mbii‚Äôanee:] mee…óee Lepte cumoowe nge."
  22,23,"Pellet, Alla naatna …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolle mo∆ī∆īi …óin Aljannaaji no ila e ley majji caat…ólii …óin, …ďe cu…óiree ndeer ton immorde jawe kanŇče e lu'ulu'uuje koltu ma…ď…ďe on nder ton ko hariire."
  22,24,"∆Āe peewnaama fa'ade e ko laa…ďi immorde e konngol ngol, …ďe peewnaa kadi fa'ade e Laawol jettiniingol ngol."
  22,25,"Pellet, …ďeen yeddu…ďe he…ďe faddaade gah Laawol Alla ngol e Juulirde Horminnde nden, nden nde Min mba…óani …óum yim…ďe …ďen, no fota ter √Īii…ďu…óo on e mayre e liigotoo…óo on. Kala paalaa…óo oo√Īorde e mayre too√Īe, Min mee…óinat mo immorde e Lepte mu'us…óe."
  22,26,"E tuma nde Min nJippinnoo Ibraahiima nokku Suudu ndun, [Min Daali:] Wota a kafidu e Am hay e hu'unde, la…ď…ďin Suudu Am ndun fii wanngotoo…ďe …ďen e darotoo…ďe …ďen [juula] e ruk∆īoo…ďe cujja …ďen."
  22,27,"Noddin e yim…ďe …ďen fii Hajju ngun, …ďe ngarat e maa…óa ko …ďe seppoo…ďe e dow kala …óehiimba reedu, …ďe ngarat immorde e kala laawol go…ó…óungol."
  22,28,"Fii yo …ďe seedo nafoore ma…ď…ďe, …ďe njaŇčtoo Innde Alla e ndeer √Īal…ói ganndaa…ói e dow ko o arsiki …ďe kon immorde e muumi neemoraa…ói, √Īaamee e majji, √Īamminon kadi baaso …ďillii…óo on."
  22,29,"Refti yo …ďe ittu tuundi ma…ď…ďe ndi, yo …ďe kuu…ďnu takke ma…ď…ďe …óen, yo …ďe mbanngo Suudu rim…óinaa- ndu ndu."
  22,30,"∆äuum [ko njamira…óon], kala mawnin…óo Hurumji Alla …ói tawat …óuum ko mo∆ī∆īere makko ka Joomi makko. Daginanaama on neemoraa…ói …óin, si wonaa kon ko janngaa e taweede mo'on, ngo…ó…óitee co…ď…óii …ói immorde e sanamuuji, ngo…ó…óito…óon kadi konngol fenaande ngol."
  22,31,"Newanii…ďe Alla …ďe ngonaani sirkanoo…ďe Mo, kala sirkan…óo Alla no wa'ita wa si o pukkii…óo immorde ka kammu sonndu biftoo mo ma henndu ruuyida e makko [li…ďoya] e nokkure wo…ó…óunde."
  22,32,"∆äuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo hollii] kala mawnin…óo Ma'andeeji Alla …óin, pellet …óum, ko e kulol …ďer…óe …óen jeyaa."
  22,33,"No woodani on e majji nafaaji haa e dummunne innaa…óo, refti nokku majji on ko ka cuudu Ndimuru."
  22,34,"Min mba…óanii kala mofte laawol fii yo …ďe njaŇčto Innde Alla e dow ko O arsiki …ďe kon immorde e muumi neemoraa…ói. Dewetee…óo mon on ko Dewetee…óo Gooto ko KaŇčko njebbilato…óon, weltinir …óoftii…ďe …ďen."
  22,35,"∆Āeen [taw…ďe] si Alla jaŇčtaama …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen kulay, e mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen e dow kon ko he…ďi …ďe e √Īinnoo…ďe Julde nden he…ďe nafka go…ó…óum e ko Min arsiki …ďe kon."
  22,36,"E geloo…ďi [fay…ói] …óin Min mba…óanii on …ói jeyaa…óum e Ma'andeeji Alla no woodani on e majji mo∆ī∆īere, njaŇčtee Innde Alla e dow majji ko …ói saffinii…ói si becce majji …óen yanii √Īaamee immorde e majji √Īamminon kadi yonndinii…óo e wee…ďitotoo…óo, ko wano nii, Min eeltirani on …ói mbelajo'o onon on j Njaarnay."
  22,37,"Hewtoytaa Alla tebbuuli majji wonaa ∆īii∆īe majji kadi, kono heewtoy mo kulol ngol immorde e mo'on. Ko wano nii O eeltani on …ói fii yo on mawni Alla e dow ko o feewni on ko, weltin mo∆ī∆īin…ďe …ďen."
  22,38,"Pellet, Alla O solnanay(du√Īanat) …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe, pellet, Alla o yi…óaa kala kodoowo keew…óo jeddi."
  22,39,"DuŇčanaama …ďeen wonaa…ďe ha…ďeede [jo…ďtagol] sabu kam…ďe ko …ďe too√Īaa…ďe, pellet, Alla ko o kattan…óo e dow wallude …ďe."
  22,40,"∆Āeen yaltinaa…ďe ka galleeji mu'en ko aldaa e goo- nga si wonaa fii tun …ďe wi'ii: ""Joomi amen ko Alla"". Sinndo wonaano Alla du√Īirde yim…ďe …ďe yoga e ma…ď…ďe yoga, yirbinteno dewir…ói ruhbaaniyankoo…ďe …ďen e dewir…ói Annasaara en e dewir…ói Alyahuuda en e Juulir…óe …óe Innde Alla jaŇčtetee e ndeer mu'un ko heewi. ma Alla wallu …ďen walloo…ďe mo, pellet, Alla ko o cemmbu…óo Teddu…óo."
  22,41,"∆Āeen taw…ďe si Min newinanii …ďe ka leydi …ďe √Īii…ďnat Juulde nde …ďe totta askaal o …ďe njamira ko mo∆ī∆īi ko …ďe ka…óa ko boni ko Ko Alla woodani …ďattane fiyakuuji …ói."
  22,42,"Si …ďe njennii ma, gooŇč…óii yeddiino ado ma…ď…ďe yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďe e AadiŇčkoo…ďe …ďe e SamuudiŇčkoo…ďe …ďe."
  22,43,"E yim…ďe Ibraahiima …ďe e yim…ďe Luutu …ďe."
  22,44,"E yim…ďe Madyana …ďe Muusaa kadi fennaama, Mi nee…ďnani yeddu…ďe …ďen refti Mi nanngi …ďe, ko honno yagginngol Am ngol wonirnoo?"
  22,45,"No foti hewde e ce'e …óee Min kalki …óum tawi ko nde too√Īnde, hara hende ngajjii e kippudiiji majje, e woyndu jirbundu e ku…ďeeje toow…óee [eggaande]."
  22,46,"Enee, hara …ďee njhaani ka leydi sakko laatanoo…ďe …ďer…óe …ďe haqqilira …óe, ma noppi …ďe nanira …ói? Pellet, [ko woni kon] wonaa gite …óe mbumi, kono ko …ďer…óe gon…óe …óe e nder becce …óen mbumi."
  22,47,"He…ďe …óa…ď…ďire yaccinaneede Lepte …óe, [e …óuum le] Alla luutndataako fodoore makko nde. Pellet √Īallal ka Joomi maa…óa ko wano duu…ďi wuluure no limorton non."
  22,48,"No foti heewde e saare nde min nee…ďnani …óum hara kayre ko nde too√Īude, refti Mi nannginde ko fa'ade ka Am woni ruttorde nden."
  22,49,"Maaku: ""eymon yo yim…ďe, nganndee min ko mi jeertinoowo on …ďanngu…óo""."
  22,50,"∆Āeen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īi …óin no woodani …ďe haforanal e arsike teddu…óo."
  22,51,"∆Āeen yaccii…ďe [fii bonnugol] e aayeeje amen …óen, …ďe ndoŇčkintaa [Min] ko …ďen …óon woni yim…ďe Jahiimaawe ngen."
  22,52,"Min Nulaani ado maa…óa immorde e Nulaa…óo wonaa kadi Annabaajo si wonaa si o janngii Seytaane wernoto e ndeer njangin makko kin. Alla itta ko Seytaane wernii kon, refti Alla tabintina aayeeje makko …óen. Alla ko O ganndo √Ďee√Ī…óo."
  22,53,"Fii yo o wa…óuko Seytaane wernotoo ko njarraboye wonan'de …ďeen …ďe nawnaare woni ka …ďer…óe mu'uen …ďe …ďer…óe mu'uen njo'ori …ďen. Pellet, too√Īoo…ďe …ďen …ďe wonii e luural go…ó…óungal."
  22,54,"Fii yo …ďeen okkaa…ďe Ganndal ngal nganndu pellet, ko [Alqur'aanaare nden woni] Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi maa…óa …ďe gooŇč…óina nde, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen yankinanoo …óum. Pellet Alla Feewnat …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe fa'ade e Laawol Pocciingol."
  22,55,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe ceerataa he…ďe e nder sikke [fii Alqur'aana] haa Darngal ngal ara e ma…ď…ďe e juhayee maa …óum ara e ma…ď…ďe Lepte √Ďalaande sa…ótunde."
  22,56,"Laamu ngu nden √Ďande ko Alla heeranii O √Ďaawoyat hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli ko mo∆ī∆īi …óin he…ďe e ndeer Aljannaaji Neemii…ói."
  22,57,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe, …ďe penni kadi aayeeje amen …óen, …ďen …óon no woodani …ďe lepte koynooje."
  22,58,"∆Āeen fer…ďe e Laawol Alla refti …ďe waraa maa …óum …ďe maayi Alla arsikoyay …ďe arsike mo∆ī∆īo. Pellet, Alla ko KaŇčko woni …ďuri Mo∆ī∆īude Arsikoo…ďe."
  22,59,"Ma O naatnoy…ďe naatirgal ngal …ďe welaa …óum. Pellet, Alla ko O ganndu…óo Mu√Ī√Īii…óo."
  22,60,"∆äuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo], kala leptu…óo yeru ko o leptaa ko, refti bewaa e hoore-makko ma Alla wallu mo. Pellet, Alla ko O Yaafotoo…óo cuhroowo."
  22,61,"∆äuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo], ko fii pellet, Alla hono naatna jemma on e ndeer √Īalorma on, hiMo naada kadi √Īalawma on e ndeer jemma on. Pellet, Alla ko o Nanoowo ji'oowo."
  22,62,"∆äuum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo], ko fii pellet, Alla ko KaŇčko woni Goonga kan pellet, kon ko …ďe noddata gaanin makko ko …óuum woni meere nden. Pellet, ko KaŇčko woni Toowu…óo mawnu…óo on.u"
  22,63,"Enee, a tinaani won'dema Alla o jippinii ndiyam immorde ka kammuuji, leydi ndin wonti hecci…óundi? Pellet, Alla ko oNewii…óo kumpitii…óo."
  22,64,"Ko KaŇčko woodani ko woni kon ka kammuuji e ka leydi. Pellet, Alla ko KaŇčko woni Galo jettinii…óo on."
  22,65,"Enee, a tinaani wonan'dema Alla eeltani on ko woni kon ka leydi, laa…óe …óen no ndogira ka maaje Yamaruyee makko on, homo jogitii kammu ngun fii wata ngu yanu e hoore leydi ndin si wonaa e duŇčayee mkko. Pellet, Alla ko o newanii…óo yim…ďe …ďen jurmotoo…óo …óo […ďe]."
  22,66,"Ko KaŇčko woni on guurnu…óo on refiti o wara on refti o wurnitoya on. Pellet ne…ó…óaŇčke on ko o keew…óo jeddi."
  22,67,"Min mba…óanii kala mofte laawol ngol …ďe ndewata e mu'un, wata …ďe poo…óondir e maa…óa e fiyaake on, noddu fa'ade ka Joomi maa…óa. Pellet, an ha…óa e hoore Laawol Pocciingol."
  22,68,"Si …ďe mbe√Īdi ma, Maaku: ""Ko Alla woni ganndu…óo ko ngolloton kon""."
  22,69,"Alla √Ďaawat hakkunde mo'on √Ďande Darngal fii kon ko luutondirton fii mu'um."
  22,70,"Enee, a anndaani won'dema Alla homo Anndi ko woni kon ka kammu e ka leydi, pellet, …óuum no e ndery Deftere. Pellet, …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] no newanii Alla."
  22,71,"He…ďe ndewa ga Alla kon ko Dalil jippinaaka e fii mu'um, e kon ko ganndal alanaa …ďe e mu'um. Alanaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen balloowo."
  22,72,"Si jannganaama …ďe aayeeje amen …óeen …ďanngu…óe a ngandat e je'ece …ďen yeddu…ďe mettinaare he…ďe …óe…ďa yanude e …ďen jannganay…ďe …ďe aayeeje amen …óen. Maaku: ""Yo mi habru on ko …ďuri bon'de e …óum moo…óon [ko jaŇčtana…óon ko] ko Yiite ngen Alla fodii nge …ďeen yeddu…ďe bonii ruttorde."
  22,73,"Eey mon yim…ďe, yeru fiyaama ke…ótee mo, pellet …ďeen …ďe noddoton gaAlla, …ďe tagata hay mbu'ubu, hay sinndo …ďe moo…ďondiriino fii …óum. Si coongil(mbuubu)ngil jattii …ďe go…ó…óum …ďe kattantaake ja…ďtugol ngil …óum. ∆äa…ď…ďu…óo on e …óa…ď…ďaa…óo on fof no lo'i."
  22,74,"∆Āe mawniniraani Alla no O haani Mawninirde non. Pellet, Alla ko cemmbu…óo Teddu…óo."
  22,75,"Alla no su…ďoo immorde e Maleykaaji …ói Nulaa…ďe e yim…ďe …ďen kadi. Pellet, Alla ko O Nanoowo ji'oowo."
  22,76,"Homo Anndi ko woni kon yeeso ma…ď…ďe e ko woni ko …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, ko faade ka Alla fiyakuuji …óin ruttetee."
  22,77,"Eey mon yo …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe, nduk∆īee cujjon ndewon Joomi mo'on, ngollon ko mo∆ī∆īi kon mbelejo'o onon on maloyte."
  22,78,"Mba…óee Jihaadi fii Alla no Jihaadi haaniri non, KaŇčko OSu…ďiima on o mba…óanaani on …ďitteende ka nder diina, diina baaba moo…óon Ibraahiima ko KaŇčko inni on juul…ďe ko adii [ndee Alqur'aanaare] e nder mayre kadi, fii yo Nulaa…óo on laato seedo e hoore-mo'on onon kadi ngonon seeditoytoo…ďe e hoore yim…ďe …ďe. √Ďii…ďnee e Juulde nden totton askal on njogitee Alla, ko KaŇčko woni Gi…óo moo…óon mo∆ī∆īii gi…óo mo∆ī∆īii balloowo on."
